{"tid":1133242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有加拿大港人要求政府派4000 以加強他們對香港歸屬感","createTime":"2019-05-01T01:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T06:24:50.000Z","uid":144372,"like":15,"dislike":715,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"150d282b79d69ff5dd4c53d0810d80b204253880","tid":1133242,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T01:31:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20180324/vaba_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Fvan%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20180324%2Fvaba_r.htm&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=c021b51d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20180324/vaba_r.htm</a><br />\n加拿大本地組織「香港情懷」主席江大惠表示﹐為免令加國香港移民產生不必要的誤會﹐香港政府需要更加詳細解釋。<br />\n<br />\n無論如何﹐任何核實驗證﹐都花人力與金錢﹐為何不像上次一樣﹐全民派錢﹐連加國香港移民也惠及。而且﹐香港政府若讓移民共享香港繁榮的成果﹐使他們感覺仍是香港大家庭的一分子﹐可起連繫海外港人的積極作用。<br />\n<br />\n江大惠指﹐香港政府這幾年進行的「大白象」工程嚴重超支﹐又缺乏長期發展眼光和計劃﹐愈益使普羅大眾覺得﹐香港政府有大筆盈餘﹐直接派給他們更加實惠﹐更有價值。<br />\n<br />\n香港特政府表示，估計有280萬人受惠，涉款約110億元，目標是在下個財政預算案前發放款項，明年2月開始接受申請。"},{"pid":"af760531b74641a8a3daad92b512eda9c67c57f0","tid":1133242,"uid":6233,"like":430,"dislike":6,"score":424,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T01:34:51.000Z","msg":"咁不如全世界都派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a489e3f2429bad25f38b6c1eb4adc7005fc861","tid":1133242,"uid":34348,"like":9,"dislike":172,"score":-163,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T01:35:36.000Z","msg":"如果一定要揀派俾逃難者定新移蝗<br />\n咁又真係前者好少少嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ea982b57aff5db4f3901ca432622ba26799b4d","tid":1133242,"uid":8858,"like":108,"dislike":3,"score":105,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"佢係加拿大人同時又腥簡人fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e62335e830f676979de4dbdab8ef777dcff5a38","tid":1133242,"uid":147029,"like":214,"dislike":3,"score":211,"quote":{"pid":"f7a489e3f2429bad25f38b6c1